{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"SHANCHENGP6","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["After the Rain Comes the Sun\n\n<size=45>Chapter 6 - Rain Shower<\/size>",1]],"mode":1},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"bgm":"story-1","nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Fwahhh... I'm all wet now... Milord, here's a towel for you!","actor":305020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Yamashiro handed me a dry towel while drying her hair with her own towel.","dir":1},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Fusou always told me to come prepared in case it suddenly started raining. I guess it came in handy today...","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Umm... something to change into, something to change into... Here it is! Give me just a-","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Turn around without saying anything"},{"flag":2,"content":"Head for the door"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Uuu... Milord, you're also here... I-I'm sorry...","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Milord? It's still raining outside!","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Um, umm... C-come back here, it's fine, really...","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"nameColor":"#a9f548","flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]},"dir":1,"say":"All right, Milord! You can turn around now!","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Sorry, I only have enough clothes for myself... but there are still fresh towels...","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"It's a shame that I couldn't finish my dance, though...","actor":305020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"I sat next to Yamashiro and quietly ruffled her hair","dir":1},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Ehehe... why does it mean so much to me? Mm, I suppose I haven't told you before?","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"The first reason is that I want to ease some of my sister's burdens and responsibilities. The second reason is because, well, you know how Fusou and I have bad luck? Akashi said that it might be because people call us \"unlucky ships.\"","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"But I think that... as ships, even if we had an unlucky service history, we can't forget about the lives and effort of the people involved...","actor":305020},{"actorName":"{namecode:79}","bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"So, we should work hard to become happy and fortunate, to repay all those people for giving us this life...","actor":305020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"And with that, the rain began to pass.","blackBg":true,"dir":1}]}